item.title: CVE-2024-27319|2024-02-23T17:39:52.870Z -- onnx -- onnx
item.description: Versions of the package onnx before and including 1.15.0 are vulnerable to Out-of-bounds Read as the ONNX_ASSERT and ONNX_ASSERTM functions have an off by one string copy.
